  <li><strong>After the highest nutrition?</strong> <a href="#years-puppy">Years</a> (95% AADF) and <a href="#butternut-box-puppy">Butternut Box</a> (93–94%) are about as good as puppy food gets — fresh, gently cooked and grain-free.</li>
